{"tid":2320846,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★香格里拉集團稱精簡部分團隊　消息：或裁本地員工約百人","createTime":"2020-12-11T06:15:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T06:41:59.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2b485cee3142cbe3b7143df4de5663dca15ce62d","tid":2320846,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T06:15:14.000Z","msg":"本地疫情持續，酒店及旅遊業經營環境受影響。香港酒店工會昨晚（10日）於社交網站帖文稱，據香格里拉酒店集團同業消息，旗下4間酒店將裁員約100人，當中九龍香格里拉營業部各職級共裁減11人，包括九格及今旅酒店總經理。另外又透露，嘉里酒店將會成為政府指定隔離酒店。<br />\n<br />\n香港酒店工會主席徐考澧今（11日）稱，消息稱香格里拉集團主要裁走高層管理人員，包括酒店總經理、餐飲部高層，以及工程、會計、人力資源等部門職員。他稱香格里拉集團是本地酒店龍頭，憂慮其他酒店或仿傚精簡人手，跟風裁員。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2825992/【疫市裁員】香格里拉集團稱精簡部分團隊%E3%80%80消息：或裁本地員工約百人?mtc=10012\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2825992%2F%E3%80%90%E7%96%AB%E5%B8%82%E8%A3%81%E5%93%A1%E3%80%91%E9%A6%99%E6%A0%BC%E9%87%8C%E6%8B%89%E9%9B%86%E5%9C%98%E7%A8%B1%E7%B2%BE%E7%B0%A1%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E5%9C%98%E9%9A%8A%25E3%2580%2580%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%EF%BC%9A%E6%88%96%E8%A3%81%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E7%B4%84%E7%99%BE%E4%BA%BA%3Fmtc%3D10012&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqVSbRuvIKfaxuJHhOs3YWJk%3D&h=61716ea1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2825992/【疫市裁員】香格里拉集團稱精簡部分團隊%E3%80%80消息：或裁本地員工約百人?mtc=10012</a>"},{"pid":"f54199fbd70e5095675729db1621dfd5dae9d49c","tid":2320846,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T06:15:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c4dccdb2be78323e1e8259f68df69c560511395","tid":2320846,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco